high_descs: Walk over to the fridge, then turn right and walk across the room and turn right then walk over to the end of the kitchen island.
Pick up the metal table spoon off of the kitchen island.

Put the table spoon in the metal pan that is on the front left burner of the stove.
Pick up the metal pan with the spoon in it.
Walk up to the sink that is behind you in the kitchen island.
Put the pan with the spoon in it into the sink basin.
